{"tid":2497689,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大嶼山愉景灣1a/1b期部分單位Usable Floor Area 只有43方呎，再破全港新盤最細單位紀錄","createTime":"2021-04-20T16:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T00:59:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f43027e72eba594c9c42d91d74fa2a9831657468","tid":2497689,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180829/s00002/13176ff3c72d7b530e4ac5fb7e11504a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180829%2Fs00002%2F13176ff3c72d7b530e4ac5fb7e11504a.jpg&h=a89a4897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據屋宇署今年初資料顯示，上述大嶼山愉景灣1a/1b期已獲批入伙紙，部分單位Usable Floor Area最細只有43方呎，與一張加大雙人牀面積相若，再破全港新盤最細單位紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180829/s00002/13177e5ec02992dae4d05350f3074d92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180829%2Fs00002%2F13177e5ec02992dae4d05350f3074d92.jpg&h=99116704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據仲量聯行的《住宅銷售市場》報告指出，上述愉景灣1a/1b區的新發展項目最細的單位，實質銷售時的實用面積將低於90方呎，將挑戰「納米樓」面積的新低。香港興業董事總經理查懋成對此回應稱，基於一手新例所限，暫時仍未能回應有關單位消息，但就補充，這些被指實用面積不足90方呎的細單位，毗鄰將連接大單位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/618/1*1KNoo1qW8Ii2HQv5RSCXzg.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F618%2F1%2A1KNoo1qW8Ii2HQv5RSCXzg.jpeg&h=eab04a64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf637cbed6479953bfc2f0090dcb98dc916611b9","tid":2497689,"uid":36441,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"當工人房咁賣姐"},{"pid":"04c8244df2ad594c2da03267a03c72bff06f29db","tid":2497689,"uid":160986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf637cbed6479953bfc2f0090dcb98dc916611b9","tid":2497689,"uid":36441,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"當工人房咁賣姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"跟著又有d傻尻衝入黎話 衰過公屋劏房